text: Strandiata abyssinica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1935, originally under the genus Tricholamia. It is known from Ethiopia.BioLib.cz - Strandiata abyssinica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1935
